-- ArcelorMittal to Announce Inox Listing Plan Today, Echos Says
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-12-08T05:18:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-08/arcelormittal-is-likely-to-announce-inox-listing-plan-today-echos-says.html
ArcelorMittal is likely to announce
plans to list its Inox unit today as it seeks to find a merger
partner for the business, French daily Les Echos reported,
citing an unidentified person.  The listing is planned to take place in the first quarter,
the newspaper said. Inox will be managed by Bernard Fontana with
Lakshmi Mittal as chairman of the board, according to Les Echos.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  